description: Base Ecosystem is an ecological application platform based on blockchain value transmission protocol ecosystem, it improves the circulation efficiency of assets and reduces circulation costs in ecological application platform through point-to-point value links and transfers in entertainment, games, malls, finance, big data and traditional assets. Base Ecosystem is a technology upgrade from universal blockchain to professional blockchain, it builds a complete and effective ecological application platform for connection and circulation of all links in blockchain ecosystem.
name: Base Ecosystem
